            <description><![CDATA[大家昨晚跨年开心吗？几点睡的[磕到了] <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%86%AC%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9C%E5%90%8E%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%A4%A9%E7%9D%A1%E8%A7%89%E8%83%BD%E8%A1%A5%E5%9B%9E%E6%9D%A5%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%86%AC%E5%A4%A7%E5%A4%9C%E5%90%8E%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E5%A4%A9%E7%9D%A1%E8%A7%89%E8%83%BD%E8%A1%A5%E5%9B%9E%E6%9D%A5%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#熬大夜后第二天睡觉能补回来吗#</span></a> [悲催]<br><br>人的一生有三分之一是在睡眠中度过，长期缺觉会造成精力透支、反应迟钝、免疫力下降、记忆力低下等问题。想事后补觉？补不了一点<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>睡眠是不能补偿或储存的。“报复性补觉”只能稍微缓解人的疲倦状态，并不能真正补偿优质的深睡眠。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[跪了]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_guile-a8a737d3a0.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（健康中国）<img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hldyeev120j20jg0k0jt5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
